SHE HAS BEEN COVERING THE STORY.

10:10.310 --> 10:11.678
SO, THEY'RE PROPOSING A LAW.

10:11.678 --> 10:13.313
WHAT'S IN THE LAW?

10:13.313 --> 10:14.347
>> WELL, THERE ARE A VARIETY OF

10:14.347 --> 10:15.215
MEASURES.

10:15.215 --> 10:18.318
THE ONE THAT'S PROBABLY GOTTEN

10:18.318 --> 10:20.386
THE MOST ATTENTION IS A

10:20.386 --> 10:22.589
REQUIREMENT THAT MODELS WOULD

10:22.589 --> 10:23.957
HAVE TO PRESENT A DOCTOR'S

10:23.957 --> 10:25.325
CERTIFICATE SAYING THAT THEY

10:25.325 --> 10:26.593
WERE AT A HEALTHY ENOUGH WEIGHT

10:26.593 --> 10:27.627
TO WORK.

10:27.627 --> 10:30.430
AND ANYONE EMPLOYING MODELS WHO

10:30.430 --> 10:31.731
WAS EMPLOYING PEOPLE WITHOUT

10:31.731 --> 10:33.566
SUCH A CERTIFICATE WOULD BE

10:33.566 --> 10:35.768
PENALIZED, BOTH FINANCIALLY AND

10:35.768 --> 10:37.470
POTENTIALLY WITH SIX MONTHS IN

10:37.470 --> 10:38.071
JAIL.

10:38.071 --> 10:39.072
>> Sreenivasan: AND WHAT WOULD

10:39.072 --> 10:40.206
BE CONSIDERED HEALTHY?

10:40.206 --> 10:41.140
WHAT ARE SOME OF THE OTHER

10:41.140 --> 10:42.141
PROVISIONS?

10:42.141 --> 10:44.077
>> SOME OF THE OTHER PROVISIONS

10:44.077 --> 10:46.012
ARE ACTUALLY QUITE INTERESTING.

10:46.012 --> 10:47.981
ONE OF THEM IS... OUTLAWS

10:47.981 --> 10:50.683
INTERNET SITES THAT ENCOURAGE

10:50.683 --> 10:52.886
ANOREXIA, AND THAT'S SOMETHING

10:52.886 --> 10:54.454
THAT'S NOT MUCH TALKED ABOUT BUT

10:54.454 --> 10:55.955
THERE ARE SUCH SITES.

10:55.955 --> 10:57.690
THERE ARE NOT A LOT OF THEM, I

10:57.690 --> 10:59.592
DON'T THINK, BUT THEY ARE

