FIGURE-- THE FRENCH WORD IS

11:21.180 --> 11:24.484
SILHOUETTE-- LOOK HEAVIER OR

11:24.484 --> 11:26.686
THINNER THAN IT REALLY IS, THE

11:26.686 --> 11:28.888
PHOTO WOULD HAVE TO BE LABELED.

11:28.888 --> 11:31.524
SO, IT'S THREE QUITE SIGNIFICANT

11:31.524 --> 11:34.761
PROVISIONS, AND WE'LL SEE IF

11:34.761 --> 11:36.429
THEY PASS THE FRENCH SENATE,

11:36.429 --> 11:38.498
WHICH IS THE NEXT BODY THAT WILL

11:38.498 --> 11:39.666
HAVE TO LOOK AT IT.

11:39.666 --> 11:40.967
>> Sreenivasan: WHAT'S THE

11:40.967 --> 11:42.302
MODELING INDUSTRY OR THE FASHION

11:42.302 --> 11:44.504
INDUSTRY HAVE TO SAY ABOUT THIS?

11:44.504 --> 11:45.772
>> WELL, IT'S QUITE INTERESTING.

11:45.772 --> 11:47.307
THE FASHION INDUSTRY, THE BIG

11:47.307 --> 11:48.641
FASHION HOUSES-- OF WHICH, AS

11:48.641 --> 11:49.943
YOU KNOW, THERE ARE A NUMBER OF

11:49.943 --> 11:52.245
THEM HERE-- HAVE BEEN PUBLICLY

11:52.245 --> 11:54.447
VERY QUIET ABOUT IT.

11:54.447 --> 11:55.982
BUT THE UNION OF MODELING

11:55.982 --> 11:57.750
AGENCIES HAS SPOKEN UP, AND THEY

11:57.750 --> 11:59.285
FEEL THE WAY THE LAW HAS BEEN

11:59.285 --> 12:03.523
DRAFTED IS VERY UNFAIR AND

12:03.523 --> 12:04.490
INACCURATE.

12:04.490 --> 12:06.826
THE BASIS ON WHICH THE LAW IS...

12:06.826 --> 12:10.229
BEEN DONE IS THE... WHAT'S

12:10.229 --> 12:12.332
CALLED THE BODY MASS INDEX,

12:12.332 --> 12:14.067
WHICH IS AN INTERNATIONALLY USED

12:14.067 --> 12:14.801
INDEX.

12:14.801 --> 12:17.604
AND THERE'S A WEIGHT RANGE FOR

12:17.604 --> 12:19.472
NORMAL WEIGHT, FOR OVERWEIGHT,

12:19.472 --> 12:22.775
FOR OBESITY AND FOR UNDERWEIGHT.

12:22.775 --> 12:24.811
AND ALL MODELS WOULD HAVE TO BE

12:24.811 --> 12:27.947
AT LEAST WITHIN THE NORMAL

12:27.947 --> 12:29.248
WEIGHT, NOT THE UNDERWEIGHT

12:29.248 --> 12:30.083
RANGE.

12:30.083 --> 12:30.850
>> Sreenivasan: ANY DIFFERENCE

12:30.850 --> 12:31.985
BETWEEN THE FRENCH AND AMERICAN

12:31.985 --> 12:33.820
SENSIBILITIES ABOUT THIS?

12:33.820 --> 12:35.188
>> NO, I THINK, ACTUALLY, THE

12:35.188 --> 12:36.556
SENSIBILITIES ARE FAIRLY

12:36.556 --> 12:38.925
SIMILAR, BUT THE PHILOSOPHY OF

12:38.925 --> 12:40.860
GOVERNMENT IS QUITE DIFFERENT.

12:40.860 --> 12:42.495
THE FRENCH ARE QUITE WILLING TO

12:42.495 --> 12:45.098
REGULATE VERY EXTENSIVELY AND IN

12:45.098 --> 12:46.833
GREAT DETAIL MANY ASPECTS OF

12:46.833 --> 12:51.371
LIFE AND... AND USE THE POWERS

12:51.371 --> 12:53.206
OF GOVERNMENT TO DO THAT, AND

12:53.206 --> 12:54.941
AMERICANS ARE MUCH MORE

12:54.941 --> 12:56.309
RELUCTANT TO REGULATE.

12:56.309 --> 12:57.243
I THINK, ON THIS, THEY'RE

12:57.243 --> 12:58.611
WILLING TO BE A BIT MORE

12:58.611 --> 12:59.545
PRESCRIPTIVE.

12:59.545 --> 13:00.313
>> Sreenivasan: AND SO, WHAT DO

13:00.313 --> 13:01.414
SAY THEY IS THE CONNECTION

13:01.414 --> 13:03.683
BETWEEN THE IMAGES THAT A YOUNG

13:03.683 --> 13:06.285
WOMAN SEES AND HER LIKELIHOOD TO

13:06.285 --> 13:07.920
BE ANOREXIC, WHICH IS SOMETIMES

13:07.920 --> 13:09.922
A PSYCHOLOGICAL DISORDER, RIGHT?

13:09.922 --> 13:11.691
>> YES, IT'S VERY OFTEN, IF NOT

13:11.691 --> 13:12.959
ALWAYS, A PSYCHOLOGICAL

13:12.959 --> 13:13.960
DISORDER.

13:13.960 --> 13:15.862
WELL, HERE, I THINK THIS IS

13:15.862 --> 13:19.565
WHERE IT'S QUITE CONFUSING.

13:19.565 --> 13:21.634
IT'S NOT CLEAR WHAT THE BASIS

13:21.634 --> 13:24.303
WAS FOR... FOR TARGETING THE

13:24.303 --> 13:26.539
FASHION INDUSTRY.

13:26.539 --> 13:27.573
WHEN I AT LEAST SPOKE WITH

13:27.573 --> 13:29.942
PSYCHIATRISTS ABOUT THIS, THEY

13:29.942 --> 13:31.644
ALL SAY THAT THERE ARE SO MANY

13:31.644 --> 13:33.813
FACTORS THAT GO INTO A YOUNG

13:33.813 --> 13:37.150
WOMAN CHOOSING OR SLIPPING INTO

13:37.150 --> 13:39.018
A STATE WHERE SHE... SHE STARVES

13:39.018 --> 13:40.286
HERSELF.

13:40.286 --> 13:42.221
AND SO, IT'S NOT REALLY CLEAR

13:42.221 --> 13:45.525
THAT DOING THIS WILL HAVE A... A

13:45.525 --> 13:47.994
VERY MEASURABLE EFFECT, BUT MORE

13:47.994 --> 13:50.029
THAT IT CREATES SORT OF

13:50.029 --> 13:52.532
DIFFERENT RESPECTED BODY IMAGES

13:52.532 --> 13:54.534
OTHER THAN ONES THAT ARE... THAT

13:54.534 --> 13:58.004
ARE OFTEN VERY SERIOUSLY THIN,

13:58.004 --> 13:59.205
WHICH IS WHAT MANY OF THE

13:59.205 --> 14:00.740
FASHION MODELS WHO ARE, OF

14:00.740 --> 14:02.241
COURSE, VERY MUCH A PART OF THE

14:02.241 --> 14:05.478
PARIS SCENE ARE AND HAVE TO BE

14:05.478 --> 14:06.713
IN ORDER TO GET... TO GET WORK.

14:06.713 --> 14:07.580
>> Sreenivasan: ALL RIGHT,

14:07.580 --> 14:08.514
ALISSA RUBIN OF THE "NEW YORK

14:08.514 --> 14:09.682
TIMES," THANKS SO MUCH.

14:09.682 --> 14:11.217
>> THANK YOU.

14:19.826 --> 14:21.728
>> Sreenivasan: AND NOW, TO OUR

14:21.728 --> 14:22.562
SIGNATURE SEGMENT.

14:22.562 --> 14:24.163
ON THIS EASTER WEEKEND, WE TAKE

14:24.163 --> 14:25.965
YOU TO JERUSALEM, WHERE NEW

14:25.965 --> 14:27.667
ARCHAEOLOGICAL FINDINGS ARE

14:27.667 --> 14:29.435
SPURRING A RENEWED DEBATE ABOUT

14:29.435 --> 14:32.205
THE FINAL HOURS OF JESUS' LIFE.

14:32.205 --> 14:34.407
JUST WHERE WAS HE PUT ON TRIAL

14:34.407 --> 14:35.808
AND PARADED BEFORE BEING

14:35.808 --> 14:36.809
CRUCIFIED?

14:36.809 --> 14:37.977
IT'S NOT JUST AN ACADEMIC

14:37.977 --> 14:38.611
QUESTION.

14:38.611 --> 14:40.012
MILLIONS OF CHRISTIAN PILGRIMS

14:40.012 --> 14:41.114
FROM AROUND THE WORLD HAVE

14:41.114 --> 14:42.749
RETRACED THE ROUTE OVER THE

14:42.749 --> 14:45.017
YEARS KNOWN AS THE VIA DOLOROSA,

14:45.017 --> 14:46.586
BUT SOME SAY THE LATEST FINDINGS

14:46.586 --> 14:48.254
SUGGEST THEY'VE BEEN WALKING THE

14:48.254 --> 14:49.188
WRONG WAY.

14:49.188 --> 14:50.289
NEWSHOUR SPECIAL CORRESPONDENT

14:50.289 --> 14:53.025
MARTIN FLETCHER EXPLAINS.

14:53.025 --> 14:55.128
>> Reporter: FOR CENTURIES,

14:55.128 --> 14:57.096
CHRISTIAN PILGRIMS HAVE COME TO

14:57.096 --> 14:58.731
JERUSALEM TO RETRACE THE LAST

14:58.731 --> 15:00.900
HOURS OF JESUS' LIFE, WALKING

15:00.900 --> 15:02.402
THE TRADITIONAL STATIONS OF THE

15:02.402 --> 15:04.470
CROSS ON THE VIA DOLOROSA, OR

15:04.470 --> 15:06.105
WAY OF SUFFERING.

15:06.105 --> 15:07.540
THE BIGGEST CROWDS COME ON GOOD

15:07.540 --> 15:08.908
FRIDAY, BUT YOU'LL FIND PILGRIMS

15:08.908 --> 15:11.010
HERE EVERY DAY OF THE YEAR.

15:11.010 --> 15:11.944
THE HOODS ARE VISITING FROM

15:11.944 --> 15:13.312
UPSTATE NEW YORK.

15:13.312 --> 15:14.847
>> I JUST WANTED TO SEE WHERE

15:14.847 --> 15:15.948
THE DIFFERENT STATIONS WERE AND

15:15.948 --> 15:16.849
WHAT THEY REPRESENT.

15:16.849 --> 15:17.817
I'VE ALWAYS HEARD ABOUT THE

15:17.817 --> 15:19.185
STATIONS OF THE CROSS BUT NEVER

15:19.185 --> 15:21.521
REALLY UNDERSTOOD IT.

15:21.521 --> 15:22.622
>> I'M FOLLOWING THE STATIONS OF

15:22.622 --> 15:25.291
THE CROSS FROM ONE THROUGH 14.

15:25.291 --> 15:26.058
>> Reporter: AT THE FIFTH

15:26.058 --> 15:26.993
STATION OF THE CROSS, WHERE

15:26.993 --> 15:28.661
PILGRIMS LAY THEIR HANDS WHERE

15:28.661 --> 15:30.363
THEY BELIEVE JESUS RESTED HIS

15:30.363 --> 15:32.331
HAND, WE MET KEN COSTA FROM

15:32.331 --> 15:33.166
INDIA.

15:33.166 --> 15:34.367
>> VERY SPIRITUAL.

15:34.367 --> 15:35.968
I FELT THAT I WAS TOUCHING

15:35.968 --> 15:37.403
JESUS' HAND.

15:37.403 --> 15:38.938
AND SINCE IT'S IMPRINTED HERE,

15:38.938 --> 15:40.206
AS THIS IS THE FIFTH STATION

15:40.206 --> 15:42.341
WHERE SIMON OF CYRENE HELPED

15:42.341 --> 15:44.644
JESUS, SO MY BELIEF IS THAT THIS

15:44.644 --> 15:46.078
WAS THE WAY.

15:46.078 --> 15:47.113
>> Reporter: BUT WAS IT?

15:47.113 --> 15:48.881
RECENTLY REVEALED DISCOVERIES ON

15:48.881 --> 15:50.082
THE OTHER SIDE OF THE CITY--

15:50.082 --> 15:51.918
REMNANTS OF AN ANCIENT PALACE

15:51.918 --> 15:53.553
WHICH JUST MAY BE THE TRUE SITE

15:53.553 --> 15:55.254
OF THE TRIAL OF JESUS-- IS

15:55.254 --> 15:56.756
RENEWING DEBATE ABOUT THE TRUE

15:56.756 --> 15:58.691
ROUTE OF THE VIA DOLOROSA.

15:58.691 --> 15:59.926
THIS IS THE ROUTE OF THE CURRENT

15:59.926 --> 16:01.861
VIA DOLOROSA, GOING FROM EAST TO

16:01.861 --> 16:03.563
WEST, ENDING AT THE CHURCH OF

16:03.563 --> 16:04.897
THE HOLY SEPULCHRE.

16:04.897 --> 16:06.833
THAT'S THE WAY MILLIONS OF

16:06.833 --> 16:07.733
CHRISTIAN PILGRIMS OVER THE

16:07.733 --> 16:09.235
YEARS HAVE FOLLOWED IN THE

16:09.235 --> 16:10.536
FOOTSTEPS OF CHRIST.

16:10.536 --> 16:11.704
BUT THERE'S ARCHAEOLOGICAL

16:11.704 --> 16:13.339
EVIDENCE THAT THEY'VE GOT IT ALL

16:13.339 --> 16:15.341
WRONG, THAT THE REAL HISTORICAL

16:15.341 --> 16:16.909
VIA DOLOROSA ENDS AT THE HOLY

16:16.909 --> 16:18.811
CHURCH BUT THAT IT SHOULD START

16:18.811 --> 16:20.713
MORE THAN A HALF MILE WAY ON THE

16:20.713 --> 16:22.415
WEST SIDE OF THE CITY, NEAR THE

16:22.415 --> 16:24.350
TOWER OF DAVID MUSEUM.

16:24.350 --> 16:26.118
THIS IS ONE VERY SPECIAL STREET

16:26.118 --> 16:27.253
NAME, ISN'T IT?

16:27.253 --> 16:29.789
VIA DOLOROSA?

16:29.789 --> 16:31.123
TO UNDERSTAND BETTER, WE VISITED

16:31.123 --> 16:32.425
WITH FRANCISCAN FATHER

16:32.425 --> 16:34.193
ALESSANDRO CONIGLIO.

16:34.193 --> 16:35.027
CHRISTIANS, WHEN THEY COME TO

16:35.027 --> 16:38.364
JERUSALEM, I IMAGINE EVERYONE--

16:38.364 --> 16:41.267
EVERY SINGLE ONE-- WALKS THE VIA

16:41.267 --> 16:41.901
DOLOROSA.

16:41.901 --> 16:42.501
>> YES.

16:42.501 --> 16:44.036
>> Reporter: WHY?

16:44.036 --> 16:45.171
>> BECAUSE THIS IS THE PATH THAT

16:45.171 --> 16:47.006
JESUS WALKED.

16:47.006 --> 16:47.907
IT'S A UNIQUE EXPERIENCE.

16:47.907 --> 16:50.042
>> Reporter: HE TOOK US TO THE

16:50.042 --> 16:51.244
VERY START OF THE TRADITIONAL

16:51.244 --> 16:52.712
VIA DOLOROSA.

16:52.712 --> 16:54.213
EACH OF THE 14 STATIONS IS

16:54.213 --> 16:55.715
MARKED WITH NUMBERS TO HELP

16:55.715 --> 16:57.383
PILGRIMS FIND THEM.

16:57.383 --> 16:58.718
SO, ACTUALLY, THE FIRST STATION

16:58.718 --> 16:59.986
OF THE CROSS IS IN A MUSLIM

16:59.986 --> 17:01.320
BOYS' SCHOOL.

17:01.320 --> 17:03.289
>> YES.

17:03.289 --> 17:04.056
>> Reporter: A SCHOOL NOW, BUT,

17:04.056 --> 17:05.391
AT THE TIME OF JESUS, IT WAS THE

17:05.391 --> 17:07.293
ANTONIA FORTRESS WHERE IT'S LONG

17:07.293 --> 17:08.461
BEEN BELIEVED THE TRIAL OF JESUS

17:08.461 --> 17:09.829
TOOK PLACE.

17:09.829 --> 17:11.364
>> THIS IS THE MOST IMPORTANT

17:11.364 --> 17:13.733
PLACE FOR US BECAUSE HERE JESUS

17:13.733 --> 17:15.968
STARTED HIS PASSION.

17:15.968 --> 17:19.438
HERE HE WAS JUDGED BY PILATE.

17:19.438 --> 17:20.473
>> Reporter: THE SECOND STATION,

17:20.473 --> 17:21.641
ACROSS THE STREET IN TWO

17:21.641 --> 17:23.409
FRANCISCAN SHRINES, IS WHERE

17:23.409 --> 17:25.478
TRADITION HAS IT JESUS TAKES UP

17:25.478 --> 17:26.879
THE CROSS AND IS FLOGGED BY

17:26.879 --> 17:28.447
SOLDIERS.

17:28.447 --> 17:30.116
STATION THREE: JESUS FALLS FOR

17:30.116 --> 17:31.884
THE FIRST TIME.

17:31.884 --> 17:33.786
STATION FOUR: JESUS MEETS HIS

17:33.786 --> 17:34.887
MOTHER.

17:34.887 --> 17:36.756
STATION FIVE: SIMON HELPS JESUS

17:36.756 --> 17:38.357
CARRY THE CROSS.

17:38.357 --> 17:39.225
THAT'S ALSO WHERE WE SEE

17:39.225 --> 17:41.193
PILGRIMS TOUCHING THE WALL.

17:41.193 --> 17:43.296
STATION SIX: VERONICA WIPES THE

17:43.296 --> 17:44.997
FACE OF JESUS.

17:44.997 --> 17:46.599
HE FALLS FOR THE SECOND TIME AT

17:46.599 --> 17:48.634
STATION SEVEN AND COMFORTS THE

17:48.634 --> 17:50.069
WOMEN OF JERUSALEM AT STATION

17:50.069 --> 17:51.437
EIGHT.

17:51.437 --> 17:52.905
NUMBER NINE: JESUS FALLS FOR THE

17:52.905 --> 17:55.408
THIRD TIME AT THIS ROMAN PILLAR.

17:55.408 --> 17:57.009
THE LAST STATIONS, TEN TO 14,

17:57.009 --> 17:58.044
ARE INSIDE THE CHURCH OF THE

17:58.044 --> 17:59.845
HOLY SEPULCHRE, BELIEVED TO BE

17:59.845 --> 18:01.847
THE EXACT PLACE WHERE JESUS IS

18:01.847 --> 18:04.650
CRUCIFIED, DIES AND IS BURIED.

18:04.650 --> 18:06.118
THE SITE WAS IDENTIFIED BACK IN

18:06.118 --> 18:07.887
THE FOURTH CENTURY BY HELENA,

18:07.887 --> 18:09.388
MOTHER OF CONSTANTINE, THE FIRST

18:09.388 --> 18:11.090
CHRISTIAN ROMAN EMPEROR.

18:11.090 --> 18:12.458
PILGRIMS HAVE WORSHIPPED HERE

18:12.458 --> 18:13.926
EVER SINCE.

18:13.926 --> 18:15.027
BUT ON THE WESTERN SIDE OF THE

18:15.027 --> 18:16.562
OLD CITY, AT THE TOWER OF DAVID

18:16.562 --> 18:18.664
MUSEUM, WE MET ARCHAEOLOGIST

18:18.664 --> 18:20.366
SHIMON GIBSON, WHO GAVE US A

18:20.366 --> 18:21.734
LOOK AT THE EVIDENCE IN A BRAND

18:21.734 --> 18:23.669
NEW EXHIBIT THAT CHALLENGES THE

18:23.669 --> 18:25.137
EXISTING ROUTE OF THE VIA

18:25.137 --> 18:26.405
DOLOROSA.

18:26.405 --> 18:27.473
>> SO, THIS IS IT.

